These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, spanish
1. the british is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Nationality   | spanish | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | parkour |

 #################################

 
